import React from 'react'
import { FaPlus } from 'react-icons/fa';

const AddItem = () => {
  return (
    <form className='addForm'>
        <label htmlFor='addItem'>Add item</label>
        <input
            autoFocus
            id='addItem'
            type='text'
            placeholder='Add Item'
            required
        />
        <button
            type='submit'
            aria-label='Add Items'
        >
            <FaPlus />
        </button>
    </form>
  )
}

export default AddItem
